# OYE STORIES — Feature Updates

Update the OYE STORIES web app with profile picture editing, an About Writer section, and Love Stories category removal.

## Proposed Changes

### Profile Picture Edit Functionality

The HTML admin settings UI already exists in [index.html](file:///c:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Desktop/dust/storybook-app/index.html) (lines 182–231) with logo/writer upload inputs and reset buttons, but **no JS handlers or CSS styles** exist yet.

#### [MODIFY] [app.js](file:///c:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Desktop/dust/storybook-app/app.js)

- Add `STORAGE_KEYS` entries: `LOGO_IMG` and `WRITER_IMG`
- Add DOM element references for: `logoUpload`, `writerUpload`, `resetLogo`, `resetWriter`, `logoPreview`, `writerPreview`, `saveWriterInfo`, `writerNameSetting`, `writerDescSetting`
- Add `handleImageUpload(inputEl, previewEl, storageKey)` — reads file via `FileReader`, converts to base64, saves to localStorage, updates preview
- Add `loadSavedImages()` — on init, loads saved logo/writer images from localStorage and applies them to homepage + admin preview
- Add `resetImage(storageKey, previewEl, defaultSrc)` — removes from localStorage and resets to default
- Add `saveWriterInfo()` — saves writer name/description to localStorage, updates homepage writer section
- Bind event listeners for `logoUpload`, `writerUpload`, `resetLogo`, `resetWriter`, `saveWriterInfo`

#### [MODIFY] [style.css](file:///c:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Desktop/dust/storybook-app/style.css)

- Add complete CSS for `.settings-section`, `.settings-title`, `.settings-grid`, `.settings-card`, `.settings-card-header`, `.settings-preview`, `.settings-img`, `.upload-btn`, `.btn-sm`
- Responsive grid for settings cards

---

