- Add an "About the Writer" section between the writer profile and the search bar on the homepage, with info about Dasari Srikanth (achievements, passion, storytelling skills)
- Add an editable textarea for the About Writer content in Admin Dashboard settings

#### [MODIFY] [app.js](file:///c:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Desktop/dust/storybook-app/app.js)

- Add `STORAGE_KEYS.ABOUT_WRITER`
- Load/save the about text from localStorage
- Admin can edit and save the about writer text

#### [MODIFY] [style.css](file:///c:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Desktop/dust/storybook-app/style.css)

- Add styling for `.about-writer` section (decorative card with gradient border)

