## Verification Plan

### Browser Testing

Open the app in a browser and verify:

1. **Profile Pictures**: In Admin Panel, upload a new logo → preview updates → reload page → logo persists. Upload writer photo → same. Click Reset → images revert. Save writer name/title → homepage updates.
2. **About Writer**: Homepage shows "About the Writer" section with Dasari Srikanth info. Admin panel shows editable textarea. Edit and save → homepage updates. Reload → persists.
3. **Love Stories Removed**: No "ప్రేమ కథలు" pill on homepage. No love option in story form. No love stories in grid. Category filter doesn't show love.
4. **Existing Features**: Stories display, search works, read view works, theme toggle works, admin login/logout works, add/edit/delete stories work.
